About World Trade Center Nauroji Nagar
The World Trade Centers Association (WTCA) actively promotes trade and investment prospects for developers of commercial real estate, economic development entities, and multinational corporations seeking to establish global connections while thriving in local markets. As an international nexus, the association facilitates a network of global relationships, distinguished properties, and comprehensive trade offerings unified under a prestigious brand.

With a vision to emerge as the premier global brand for facilitating international business ties and commerce, the WTCA aims to leverage its exclusive network of branded properties and integrated trade services. Its mission is centred on broadening the scope and enhancing the calibre of its worldwide WTCA network.

Project Skyline
A premium parcel of land spanning 24.96 acres, encompassing Nauroji Nagar in the southern region of New Delhi, is poised to host 12 multi-storied Corporate Office Towers, dominating the commercial landscape of the city. The property offers strategic connectivity, situated with frontage on Africa Avenue and Ring Road, both prominent thoroughfares in New Delhi. Africa Avenue serves as a link between Palm Marg in the south and Diplomatic Enclave in the north. Additionally, the property enjoys proximity to Bhikaji Cama Place to the west and borders Safdarjung Enclave to the south.

Pro-Business Environment
Spread across 12 grand towers, the World Trade Center Nauroji Nagar boasts over 30 lakh square feet of premium commercial space. Adorned with an elegant glass facade and metal cladding, the complex exudes a futuristic appeal. The customizable interiors and spacious lobby are designed to enhance tranquillity and overall well-being.

Employment within the Commercial Complex at Nauroji Nagar promises to elevate productivity significantly. With centralized air conditioning and integrated Building Management Systems, occupants are assured of unparalleled comfort, convenience, and safety. Incorporating high-end Environment-Friendly specifications is poised to infuse positive energy throughout the building. Thoughtfully designed spaces that seamlessly blend functionality with leisure contribute to stress reduction. Furthermore, landscaped open areas and terraces offer a serene ambience conducive to relaxation.

State-of-the-Art Facilities

  • Dedicated Space for Cultural Activities
  • Auditoria, Board Rooms
  • Conference Rooms
  • Multi-Layered Security
  • F & B Courts
  • Centrally Air-conditioned
  • Health Centres
  • Three Level Basement Parking

Key Highlights
12 Towers (30 lakh sq.ft.)
Parking Space for 8000 Cars
Green Building
Composite Structure Technique
Power Back-up

Safety & Security

  • Intelligent addressable detectors
  • Fire alarm panel based on microprocessor
  • Hooters for early warning of the people for evacuation
  • Public address system to facilitate faster and more effective evacuation
  • External & Internal hydrants, dedicated water tank for fire and automatic sprinkler systems
  • Ventilated stairways for smoke-free evacuation
  • Multiple evacuation points and refuge platforms
  • Security monitoring at every strategic access point
  • Emergency control of elevators, HVAC systems and automatic rescue devices in elevators
  • Equipped with CCTV cameras
  • Fire detector system
  • Access control & boom barrier

Royale Realtors India | South Delhi’s Top Luxury Real Estate Agents

Follow @royalerealtorsindia on social media

Check out our other properties here.

About Royale Realtors India
Royale Realtors India is a luxury real estate company. We help High Networth Individuals, Top Industrialists, NRIs, MNCs, and Investors by offering Personalised Real Estate bouquet services in Prime Locations of SOUTH DELHI through Premium Luxury Listings of high-end Properties, like Villas, Land, Apartments, builder floors, flats, bungalows, duplexes, triplexes or Offices. Founded In 1990, We’ve spent decades excelling in the competitive landscape of South Delhi real estate, establishing a class reputation as expert advisors serving boutique-style solutions to a niche clientele.

Our business is built on communication, dedication, and transparency. The processes we have mastered have helped us to rise to the level of the best real estate consultants In South Delhi. With our sharp knowledge of the local market, We’ve helped over 500 families & many multinational companies in South Delhi find their desired properties, and We are confident we can help you find yours too, or in your family or for your organization.

Our Serving Areas
Please feel free to contact us for sale, purchase, leasing, to-let, and collaborations. Our serving areas are Anand Lok, Anand Niketan, Chanakyapuri, Chattarpur, Chirag Enclave, Chittaranjan Park, Connaught Place, Defence Colony, East Of Kailash, Friends Colony, Gk-1, Gk-2, Golf Links, Gulmohar Park, Hauz Khas, Hauz Khas Enclave, Hemkunt Colony, Jangpura Extension, Jor Bagh, Kailash Colony, Kailash Hills, Lajpat Nagar, Lutyens Delhi, Maharani Bagh, Malcha Marg, Malviya Nagar, Mehrauli, Navjivan Vihar, Neeti Bagh, Nehru Enclave, Nehru Place, Nizamuddin East & West, Pamposh Enclave, Panchsheel Park, RK Puram, Safdarjung Development Area, Saket, Sarvodaya Enclave, Sarvpriya Vihar, Shanti Niketan, South Extension, Uday Park, Vasant Kunj, Vasant Vihar, and Westend.
